OL,7,FCounselling in the Community helps
OL,8,Faround 100 people a week - but they
OL,9,Fsay they're struggling to provide
OL,10,F"vital" support after their main hub
OL,11,Fwas damaged by a storm. The founder
OL,12,Fhas been speaking to Tim Scott.
OL,14,FA charity honoured with the King's
OL,15,FAward for Voluntary Service says they
OL,16,Fare "in crisis" after a huge storm
OL,17,Fcaused thousands of pounds worth of
OL,18,Fdamage to their building.
