OL,7,FCounselling in the Community received
OL,8,Fthe highest award given to local
OL,9,Fvolunteering groups in the UK for
OL,10,Foffering life-changing support and
OL,11,Fcounselling to children and adults in
OL,12,Fthe Blackpool area.
OL,14,FBut they are currently unable to
OL,15,Fcelebrate after Storm Amy caused major
OL,16,Fdamage to the roof of its main hub on
OL,17,FWaterloo Road in South Shore in
OL,18,FOctober.
