OL,5,Cbuilding
OL,7,FRooms once used for counselling,
OL,8,Ffundraising events and community
OL,9,Fwellbeing activities have also
OL,10,Fsustained significant structural
OL,11,Fdamage caused by gallons of water
OL,12,Fpouring in from the roof.
OL,14,FStuart Hutton-Brown, the founder of
OL,15,Fthe charity, said: "We're doing all we
OL,16,Fcan to raise the money to fix the roof.
