OL,3,CAward-winning charity 'in crisis'
OL,4,Cafter storm causes major damage to
OL,5,Cbuilding
OL,7,F"We have 100 people a week that use
OL,8,Fthe facility that are having to find
OL,9,Fsomewhere else to go - we can try to
OL,10,Fplace them at another hub - but the
OL,11,Farea is very deprived and some people
OL,12,Fdon't have access to wi-fi or laptops.
OL,14,F"We just need to get back open as soon
OL,15,Fas possible."
