OL,4,Cafter storm causes major damage to
OL,5,Cbuilding
OL,7,FThe charity, which also has a base in
OL,8,FThornton-Cleveleys and Bispham, has
OL,9,Fset up a fundraiser to fix the roof
OL,10,Fbut Stuart says continued rainfall is
OL,11,Fincreasing repair costs and delaying
OL,12,Ftheir ability to safely reopen.
OL,14,FIt is hoped the insurance company will
OL,15,Fcover some of the damage but the
OL,16,Fcharity needs to find at least #20,000
OL,17,Fto replace the roof and rebuild the
OL,18,Fbuilding's structure.
