OL,7,FStuart says being recognised with the
OL,8,FKing's Award is the "light at the end
OL,9,Fof the tunnel" after a terrible couple
OL,10,Fof months for the charity.
OL,12,FThe award celebrates and promotes the
OL,13,Fwork of those who help others in their
OL,14,Fcommunity, honouring work across a
OL,15,Frange of areas including heritage,
OL,16,Fculture, wellbeing and social support.
OL,18,FHe added: "It is a huge thank you.
OL,19,FIt's a huge thank you to the 100 plus
OL,20,Fvolunteers who work for us.
